sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant React as "React Frontend"
    participant Main as "Main Server"
    participant Cache as "Main Cache (CompanyId -> WorkerNodeId)"
    participant DB as "Main SQLite (Root tier)"
    participant Worker as "Worker Node (primary)"

    Note over React,Worker: Phase 1 — Endpoint discovery (post-login)
    React->>Main: "POST /API/V1/Auth/Login (Email, Password)"
    Main->>DB: "SELECT CompanyId, WorkerNodeId FROM UserDirectory"
    Main->>Cache: "GET MainWorker:Company:{id}:WorkerNodeId"
    alt cache miss
        Main->>DB: "SELECT WorkerNodeEndpoint WHERE IsBackup=0"
        DB-->>Main: "WorkerNodeEndpoint"
        Main->>Cache: "SET TTL=CompanyToWorkerTtlSeconds (default 900s)"
    end
    Main->>Worker: "POST /API/V1/Auth/VerifyCredential (proxy)"
    Worker-->>Main: "200 (Verified, Has2FAEnabled)"
    Main->>Main: "Mint RS256 worker JWT (sub, cmp, wnk, aud=worker, exp, kid)"
    Main-->>React: "200 { WorkerEndpoint, WorkerJwt, JwtExpiresAt }"

    Note over React: JWT held in-memory only (useRef). Never localStorage / cookie / URL.

    Note over React,Worker: Phase 2 — Direct calls (Main bypassed)
    React->>Worker: "GET /API/V1/Company/{slug} (Authorization: Bearer JWT)"
    Worker->>Worker: "Verify RS256 sig, kid, exp(skew=60s), aud, wnk, iss"
    Worker-->>React: "200 (data)"

    Note over React,Worker: Phase 3 — Endpoint refresh (JWT near-expiry or 401)
    React->>Main: "POST /API/V1/Auth/RefreshEndpoint (session cookie)"
    Main->>Cache: "GET CompanyId -> WorkerNodeId"
    alt worker reassigned
        Main->>DB: "Re-resolve mapping and invalidate stale cache"
    end
    Main->>Main: "Mint fresh worker JWT"
    Main-->>React: "200 { WorkerEndpoint, WorkerJwt, JwtExpiresAt }"
    React->>Worker: "Retry original request with new JWT"
    Worker-->>React: "200 (data)"
